OL,6,FThe solicitor for the victims of the
OL,7,FSouthport stabbings has said that
OL,8,Fjustice is only part of the grieving
OL,9,Fprocess, six months on from the attack.
OL,11,FThree girls, Elsie Dot Stancombe,
OL,12,Fseven, Bebe King, six, and Alice Da
OL,13,FSilva Aguiar, nine, and all lost their
OL,14,Flives in the attack that shook the
OL,15,Fseaside town on the 29 July 2024.
OL,17,FSara Stanger, Solicitor at Bond Turner
OL,18,Fsaid: "From talking to the families,
OL,19,Fyou get such a real sense of who the
OL,20,Fgirls were.
