OL,6,F"The big personalities that they had
OL,7,Fand the huge whole that they have
OL,8,Fleft."
OL,10,FAxel Rudakubana, 18, was sentenced to
OL,11,F52 years in prison for the murder of
OL,12,Fthe three girls and the attempted
OL,13,Fmurder of 10 others, including two
OL,14,Fadults, at a Taylor Swift-themed dance
OL,15,Fclass.
OL,17,FMs Stanger continued: "Following the
OL,18,Fguilty plea, there was some relief
OL,19,Fthat they wouldn't have to go through
OL,20,Fwhat could have been four weeks of
OL,21,Fcriminal trial.
