OL,6,F"I think the sentencing was incredibly
OL,7,Fshocking for everyone listening to it.
OL,8,FBut I mean, the families were
OL,9,Fdevastated in relation to the further
OL,10,Fdetails that were released.
OL,12,F"But even the most hardened of police
OL,13,Fofficers were shocked by what came out
OL,14,Fduring the sentencing."
OL,16,FRudakubana was known to multiple
OL,17,Fagencies over a number of years,
OL,18,Fincluding counter-terrorism.
